2265
04:18:05.500 --> 04:18:17.500
There's a lot of driving on back roads and up mountains and dirt roads to get to the clients that rely on these services.

2266
04:18:17.500 --> 04:18:24.000
There's workers comp, payroll taxes, benefits, you know, the agency's professional liability insurance.

2267
04:18:24.000 --> 04:18:34.000
There's training, including, you know, the recently mandated six hours of dementia training a year and four hours in continuing.

2268
04:18:34.000 --> 04:18:39.000
It's a good thing, but there's a cost to it.

2269
04:18:39.000 --> 04:18:47.500
And agencies are obligated by the legislature to pay their staff while they're going through that training.

2270
04:18:47.500 --> 04:18:57.500
There's criminal background tests and TB tests, and now COVID tests that need to be done on a regular basis.

2271
04:18:57.500 --> 04:19:04.500
