2652
05:10:22.500 --> 05:10:39.500
It also is required to be, the whole model is around being home-like and normal so that children are, you know, feel like they're living a normal life and that encourages them to flourish.

2653
05:10:39.500 --> 05:10:45.500
There's a treatment milieu that emphasizes rehabilitation and really healthy child development.

2654
05:10:45.500 --> 05:10:49.500
So I know the chairman asked Thank you.

2655
05:10:49.500 --> 05:10:55.500
There's a treatment milieu that emphasizes rehabilitation and really healthy child development.

